They've added the concrete barriers

236
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,000
on the side of the road.

237
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,000
That's a much safer environment.

238
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,000
But as a citizen, I was able to say,

239
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,000
here's what my government did.

240
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:53,000
They identified the challenge or the problem

241
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:55,000
that was a priority for the citizens.

242
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:59,000
They did actual analytic work using a GIS

243
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:02,000
to understand where they could improve on that problem.

244
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,000
They did the analysis.

245
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,000
They created a report.

246
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:08,000
They incorporated it into their capital improvement plan

247
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,000
and their process,

248
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:11,000
and they executed against it.

249
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:13,000
And all of it's available for me as a citizen

250
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,000
to watch and track.

251
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,000
